languages.text: "Что это было? Нападение прямо в доке?"
"What was that? An attack right on dock?"
languages.original_text: "Что это было? Нападение прямо в доке?"

traits.locale_text: "What was that? An attack right in the docks?"
"What was that? An attack right in the docks?"
"What was that? An attack right on the docks?"
"What was that? An attack right on the docks?"
"What was that? An attack right on Dock 1?"
"What was that? An attack right on dock?"
"What was that? An attack right on dock?"

languages.text: 「今のは一体？ドックで襲撃があったのか？」
languages.original_text: "What was that? An attack right on dock?"

traits.locale_text: 「今のは一体？ドックで襲撃があったのか？」

languages.text: “这算什么？在码头上就发动袭击？”
languages.original_text: "What was that? An attack right on dock?"

traits.locale_text: “这算什么？在码头上就发动袭击？”

languages.text: «¿Qué ha sido eso? ¿Un asalto en el propio puerto?».
languages.original_text: "What was that? An attack right on dock?"

traits.locale_text: «¿Qué ha sido eso? ¿Un asalto en el propio puerto?».

languages.text: « C'était une attaque ? En plein sur le quai ? »
languages.original_text: "What was that? An attack right on dock?"

traits.locale_text: « C'était une attaque ? En plein sur le quai ? »

languages.text: "Was war denn das? Ein Angriff direkt am Dock?"
languages.original_text: "What was that? An attack right on dock?"

traits.locale_text: "Was war denn das? Ein Angriff direkt am Dock?"

languages.text: "Bu neydi? Rıhtımın orta yerinde kim saldırır?"
languages.original_text: "What was that? An attack right on dock?"

traits.locale_text: "Bu da neydi? Rıhtımın ortasında bir saldırı mı?"
